# Changelog is append-only — both sides of any merge/rebase add entries near
# the top, which made wiki/Version-History.md conflict on essentially every
# parallel or stale-base change. The built-in `union` merge driver keeps BOTH
# sides' added lines instead of emitting a conflict, so the changelog never
# blocks a merge or rebase again. (Only valid for append-only files — do NOT
# add prose files like CLAUDE.md here, where edits replace text.)
wiki/Version-History.md merge=union
